## Phases

The project runs as **5 phases**, each driven by GSD's `/gsd:plan-phase` → `/gsd:execute-phase` → `/gsd:verify-work` → `/gsd:ship` loop.

| # | Name | SRP step(s) | Outcome |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | discover | Steps 1–3 | `model.orm.yaml` skeleton: object types + binary fact types from FKs. No constraints yet. |
| 2 | lift-explicit | Step 4 | YAML extended with explicit-source constraints (UC, mandatory, value) lifted from DDL. |
| 3 | infer | Steps 5–7 | YAML extended with sample / common-sense / llm-inferred constraints. Antipatterns flagged. |
| 4 | verify | Steps 8–9 | Verbalization emitted. User confirms LLM proposals. Verifier runs 27 rules + E1 diff. |
| 5 | translate | Step 10 | `model.py` (PyRel) emitted. |

